ActDepartment of Indian Affairs and Northern Development Act
PrecisAppointment of VALERIE GIDEON, President of the Federal Economic Development Agency for Northern Ontario, to be concurrently Deputy Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations, to be styled Deputy Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations and Northern Affairs, to hold office during pleasure, effective November 25, 2023.
